  "text": "Statistics. The P values of Student's t-test were calculated with Microsoft Excel 2010 or EZR (Jichi Medical University, Saitama, Japan) [CITATION_1] . Log-rank test was performed with EZR, a graphical user interface for R (The R Foundation for Statistical Computing, Austria).",
